# Yoga Landing Page
This is a simple and responsive Yoga landing page created with HTML and CSS. The design includes smooth transitions and animations to enhance the user experience. It is a redesigned design to enhance the skills of just looking at the design and recreating.

## Design Credit
The original UI design was created by **Young Kim**. Figma Profile: [https://www.figma.com/@youngkim5](https://www.figma.com/community/file/1229610063156797225/figma-design-responsive-yoga-website)

## Development Team
- **[Matheus Gonzalez]** - Me (https://github.com/MatheusVGonzalez)
- **Rinko** (GitHub: [@matsu129](https://github.com/matsu129))

## Features
- CSS transitions on buttons and images
- Animations on text and elements
- Responsive layout
- Toggle dark mode

## How to Use
Just open `index.html` in your browser. No installation required.

